  ('medical-tech-moex-20632', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '10歲男孩突發性腹股部劇痛，無法以一般止痛藥止痛。最可能的診斷為： 睪丸之絨毛細胞癌 (Choriocarcinoma)  精索靜脈曲張 (Varicocele) 精索扭轉 (Spermatic cord torsion)  精索水囊腫 (Hydrocele)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20633', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關急性髓性白血病 (Acute Myeloid Leukemia) 發生機制的敘述，何者最正確？ 早期髓性造血幹細胞 (Early myeloid stem cell) 過度增生所致 髓性造血幹細胞無法正常分化為較成熟的血球所致 未分化的最早期造血幹細胞過度增生所致 已成熟的髓性細胞生命週期延長，所以造血細胞堆積', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20634', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '腎臟腫瘤在顯微鏡下具有胚胎性類腎結構 (embryonic nephrogenic zone structure)，並有第11染色體上腫瘤 抑制基因之缺損。則下列何者為最可能之診斷？ 血管肌脂瘤 (Angiomyolipoma)  腎細胞癌 (Renal cell carcinoma) Wilms氏腫瘤 (Wilms’ tumor)  過渡細胞癌 (Transitional cell carcinoma)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 53, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20635', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '成人罹患睪丸腫瘤，併發淋巴腺轉移，經手術及放射線治療後未見再發，最可能是何種腫瘤？ 絨毛細胞癌 (Choriocarcinoma)  胚胎細胞癌 (Embryonal carcinoma) 精細胞瘤 (Seminoma)    卵黃囊瘤 (Yolk sac tumor)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 54, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20636', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '腎臟移植後數分鐘內即發生排斥，最可能的原因為何？ 小動脈硬化 (Arteriolar sclerosis)  腎小管間質發炎 (Tubulointerstitial inflammation) 腎間質纖維化 (Interstitial fibrosis)  血液循環中有HLA抗體存在', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20637', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種胃腫瘤最容易造成胃部無法舒張、容積減少？ 息肉型 (polypoid) 胃癌    潰瘍型 (ulcerated) 胃癌 戒環細胞 (signet ring cell) 胃癌  胃腸道間質細胞瘤 (gastrointestinal stromal tumor)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
